// RevenueCat Configuration
//
// Copy this file to RevenueCat.xcconfig and fill in your API key.
// The .xcconfig file is gitignored and must NOT be committed to version control.
//
// To obtain your API key:
// 1. Log in to the RevenueCat dashboard (https://app.revenuecat.com)
// 2. Navigate to your project > API Keys
// 3. Copy the "Apple App Store" public API key
//
// Usage in code:
//   Bundle.main.infoDictionary?["REVENUECAT_API_KEY"] as? String

REVENUECAT_API_KEY = your_revenuecat_ios_api_key_here
